以下有期徒刑\r\n。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/109%2c%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%2c549%2c20210112%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,109,交易,549,20210112,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"交易","JNO":"549","JDATE":"20210112","JTITLE":"公共危險"}